Hello! This a game based on a pygame game template demonstrated at [programarcadegames.com](http://programarcadegames.com/index.php?chapter=introduction_to_graphics).

This is a clone of the popular arcade game lunar-lander.

It demonstrates some of pythons OO tools as well as classical mechanics principles.

